<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <script>
        async function uploadFile() {
            console.log('upload..');
            const inputElement = document.getElementById('fileupload');
            let formData = new FormData();
            formData.append("file", inputElement.files[0]);
            await fetch('/data', {
                method: "POST",
                body: formData
            });
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <input id="fileupload" type="file" />
    <button onclick="uploadFile()">
        Upload
    </button>
</body>
</html>
